TEXT.S: Michael D. Higgins I 1941 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 18 a romi'ad ko kasofocan ni Michael D. Higgins, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Iceland, Ireland anini i ci Michael D. Higgins, patirengan a romi'ad i 2011 a miheca saka 11 folad saka 11 a romi'ad. I 'ayaway a 'orip Lalomaan a 'orip
